messages.text: So, uh, Anton…
Didn’t quite expect to have your men meet us at the airport, lure us in the garage...
then throw BLACK SACKS over our heads, while riding in the trunk to this SHITHOLE destination.
Ah, so you are there. And sry. My guy had to take precaution.
God, you even type in that accent
You once say you like accent. Remember those times?
No time for reminiscing. Who is this guy? You haven’t told me his name yet.
What guy?
THIS GUY YOU HAVE DOING THE JOB.
You can know him as Z.
Fine, so where are you, and what is Z’s grand plan here?
And do you think that maybe you can tell your people to offer us some fucking food?
Some pierogis? Borscht? We’re starving.
I will have them bring you food.
Yeah, so where are you then?
Z saw all the girls arrive to Saint X. We are at the perimeter.
So what the hell is this place?
It is actually not named Saint X, that is just the code name.
It is really called Bogdan Foundation and run by a man named Alexei Shevchenko.
Z says that they use it to grant money to certain businesses and
is notorious for funding illegal foreign operations.
Who is this Alexei guy?
A fake philanthropist of sorts. He has ties to your Angela Smith.
Maybe he invested money in the experiment.
Perhaps...
Okay, so how are we busting them out?
Basically, to our advantage Viktor Berdichev is meeting a Russian ambassador up the block.
So what? Who is that?
Our much hated president. Do you not read newspaper?
No, it stresses me out.
Many protestors will be showing up. So Z will get some of his men to start riot.
We slip out with girls easier that way.
You don’t think a group of 40 girls who all look alike won’t be conspicuous??
What do you mean conspicuous?
NOTICEABLE.
Oh…No - we take them out into four separate groups and spread them going in four directions.
So if there is a riot going on, how can you guarantee none of them will get hurt?
Our job is to get them out and bring them back to where you are.
Nothing better happen to Em.
Do not worry.
Okay, so who is picking me up and taking me there?
Z says no go.
What the fuck does Z mean by no go!? It’s a BIG GO!!
If they recognize you, you blow everything.
Angela Smith has never seen me up close.
She has your telephone number no?
Yes…
Then she knows everything. You must assume this.
Yeah, but since I don’t know what kind of psychopath Z is...
how do I know he’s not just going to lead the girls out and
harvest all their organs to sell on the black market!? Huh?
You need to trust me. You paid him. He is good for the money.
Anton, I have to be there. I can’t wait for you guys to MAYBE bring them back. Please.
I mean I could probably get into the building myself. I just have to call the Monkey to take down security.
We have our own Monkey.
Yeah, well if Z wants the other half of his money, I will be a part of this.
You can’t threaten Z. He will just walk away and watch American television all afternoon instead.
He gets business all the time, he doing this as favor to me, as I’m doing this favor to you.
Let me go inside, and scope the place out. You know I can do this. I’ve done it before.
And I bet you my Monkey is better than your Monkey.
Not to mention I’m sure all you slavish Ukrainian goons are fairly obvious...
Let me in. If I were in charge of being on the inside the first time, we wouldn’t even be in this situation.
Go on! Tell Z about what happened in Shenko.
Your friend stay where she is. You come.
YES. And I want to use MY Monkey.
If I being honest, our Monkey, not as good as ur monkey.
So is this a go?
Petre will drive u.
I’m not wearing the bag again, I’ll need to negotiate the plan with The Monkey.
U will need to be wearing black bag, only to certain point.
Ugh, whatever. Hold on, I’m texting the Monkey.
Z wants to know more of plan first.
I will need a woman’s suit in a size 10. Black. None of that pin-striped shit.
And I will need one of his men to show up wearing a suit, as a translator.
You trying to pitch business to Alexei to buy maybe?
Yes.
What kind of business?
I’ll google something.
No…you being from US too obvious. Not work.
You’re probably right.
SHIT.
Z will make sure you are able to slip inside.
The Monkey said there are several emergency exits.
Z says four.
When you find girls, you let Z’s men inside back. They take over from there.
And when does this riot start?
Viktor is expected 2 hours from now. The second you spot the women and let the men in...
we will create the diversion in the front.
What are the men going to do when they are inside?
Take out whoever is in the way.
If any of the hairs on any of these girls’ heads are hurt, ESPECIALLY, Emily or Adrienne’s...
The Monkey and I will take down Z’s network.
Z’s more powerful than you.
I’ll decide that when I get there.
Petre is waiting for you out front.
You don’t suppose there’s a Burger King anywhere...?
No. McDonalds.
You don’t suppose Petre would make a quick pitstop would ya?
Why, didn’t they bring you food?
It’s just a good luck ritual.
He drive you straight here.
Fine. See you soon. Don’t forget the suit. SIZE 10.
Maybe after this is all over, we go to McDonalds together...
I said no flirting.
Click below to see what happens next...
